      • replay

        public void replay(@NotNull
                   T messageHandler)
        Replays all transactions on the provided message handler.

        Note: Messages used when invoking the provided message handler may be reused. If messages are saved by the message handler, internal copies must be made to ensure proper functionality.

        Parameters:
        messageHandler - message handler to replay messages on
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if this message has not been signed before this method is called.
